lead_paragraph: Ben Stokes' death-over heroics had been crucial to England's successful World Twenty20 campaign but it took just four deliveries against Carlos Brathwaite in the final on Sunday to shatter the paceman's hard-earned reputation.

headline.print_headline: Death-Over Skills Desert Stokes in Brathwaite Assault
